
-- Features: Vis-a-vis other NoSQL database(like HBase & Cassandra) #18

  + Flexibility
  + Flexible query model
  + Native Aggregation
  + Schemaless model

-- Key characteristic #18

  + General purpose database
  + Flexible schema design
    - Attributes that can be modified on fly
  + High availability
  + Secondary indexing
  + Scalability
    - Grows horizontally
    - Sharding
  + Aggregation framework
    - Can perform ETL before data leaves MongoDB
  + Native replication
  + JSON object 
    - for storing documents
  + MapReduce
    - Not as advanced. but still useful
  + Geospatial information 

